  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model predicts absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated; 7 were formally assessed and 6 were scoped out due to epistemic constraints at MRL 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. The intended use scope — continuous-flow VAD support at 5 L/min and 120 mmHg differential pressure in adult patients — is described in the bound Claim and Requirement nodes. Decision: Accepted under the Minimal credibility profile with documented factor gaps.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cfd-hemolysis-class3-vad",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/morrison-cfd-centrifugal-pump-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-generic-pump-piv-measurements",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/morrison-hemolysis-experimental-2021"
  ],
